Add the `TransportErrorInfo` type to `chat-types.ts` and implement the `classifyTransportError` helper in `use-chat-session.ts`. Then update the hook's error state from `string | null` to `TransportErrorInfo | null`.

## 1. Add TransportErrorInfo to chat-types.ts

**File:** `apps/client/src/layers/features/chat/model/chat-types.ts`

Add the following type after the existing `ChatStatus` type:

```typescript
/** Client-side transport error classification for banner display. */
export interface TransportErrorInfo {
  heading: string;
  message: string;
  retryable: boolean;
  autoDismissMs?: number;
}
```

Update the re-export line in `use-chat-session.ts` to include `TransportErrorInfo`:

