## Acceptance Criteria

- `TransportErrorInfo` type is exported from `chat-types.ts`
- `classifyTransportError` correctly classifies SESSION_LOCKED, network, server (500-599), timeout (408), and unknown errors
- `error` state is `TransportErrorInfo | null` throughout the hook
- `stream-event-handler.ts` compiles with updated `setError` signature
- No other consumers of `error` outside ChatPanel (verify via grep)
- TypeScript compiles cleanly (`pnpm typecheck`)

